<FIRST>u i BC-Japan-Stocks     08-03 0027</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-Japan-Stocks,0027</SECOND>
<HEAD>Nikkei Stocks Down 119 Points</HEAD>
<DATELINE>TOKYO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The Nikkei Stock Average closed Thursday at
34,779.81, down 119.53 points on the Tokyo Stock Exchange.
</TEXT>
