<HEAD>Soviet Post Office Collapse Kills 11 People</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MOSCOW (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Eleven people were killed and two injured when
stone columns and balconies collapsed at Kiev's main post office
during heavy rain, officials reported Thursday.
   Rescuers using cranes and clawing with bare hands completed
their search of rubble early Thursday and found no further victims
