<HEAD>Guyana To Award Loyal Soldiers With Free Land</HEAD>
<DATELINE>GEORGETOWN, Guyana (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   President Desmond Hoyte on Thursday
said he will award free land to soldiers for their loyalty during
the last several months of strikes, shortages and food riots.
   The state-run Public Communications Agency quoted Hoyte as
